- Oh, I'm--
- What place, like, do you have?

34:39.734 --> 34:42.100
- Oh, God, God. I'm so sorry...
- Are you okay?

34:42.100 --> 34:43.467
- That I asked you to want to

34:43.500 --> 34:44.633
