38:23.667 --> 38:25.333
- [laughs]

38:25.367 --> 38:27.133
- Let's talk about
these injuries for a second.

38:27.133 --> 38:28.767
Shep, you walked
into a glass door?

38:29.000 --> 38:31.000
- Yes, I was at a party
and somebody was like,

38:31.000 --> 38:32.500
"There's a basketball court
downstairs."

38:32.533 --> 38:33.734
And I was like, "Yeah!"

38:33.767 --> 38:35.533
And I run down the stairs,

38:35.533 --> 38:37.734
and I'm talking smack
to everybody behind me.

38:37.767 --> 38:40.467
And there's just
a floor-to-ceiling glass door

38:40.500 --> 38:42.066
and I just ran right into it.

38:42.100 --> 38:44.667
- Um, had you seen a doctor yet

38:44.700 --> 38:48.000
for, uh, your finger
or did you get a splint at CVS?

38:48.000 --> 38:49.500
- No, I went to the hospital.
- You did?

38:49.533 --> 38:51.667
- Craig, it took you forever
to get it looked at.

38:51.700 --> 38:54.100
- No, but I got a splint
from the hospital.

38:54.133 --> 38:55.500
- The reason your thing's
mangled

38:55.533 --> 38:57.166
is 'cause you waited too long.

38:57.166 --> 38:59.000
- I gotta say,
I can't stop looking at that.

38:59.033 --> 39:00.700
- They fixed it.
I just--yeah, whatever.

39:00.734 --> 39:02.300
- But you know what?
I like to see that

39:02.333 --> 39:04.300
you have a physical flaw.

39:04.300 --> 39:05.533
- Thanks.
- Aww, Craig.

39:05.567 --> 39:06.767
- Aww.
- Wow.

39:07.000 --> 39:08.400
- [chuckles]
- Yeah.

39:08.433 --> 39:10.300
- Um, Sacha from Austin said,

39:10.333 --> 39:12.100
"Ashley, you were very insistent

39:12.133 --> 39:14.500
"on being invited to
Saint's second birthday party.

39:14.533 --> 39:17.300
"On what planet
do you think it's appropriate

39:17.333 --> 39:20.433
for you to even ask?"

39:20.433 --> 39:22.767
- It wasn't so much
about the birthday party.

39:23.000 --> 39:24.300
It could have been any party.

39:24.300 --> 39:26.300
It was more just
wanting to be included.

39:26.333 --> 39:29.667
- In Hilton Head, they were
really making an effort to

39:29.700 --> 39:31.166
try to make you included.

39:31.166 --> 39:33.033
I mean, they invited you
horseback riding.

39:33.066 --> 39:34.266
- But something turned.

39:34.300 --> 39:36.000
- And it was very quick.

39:36.033 --> 39:38.700
- You became feverishly obsessed

39:38.734 --> 39:40.433
with this birthday party.

39:40.467 --> 39:41.734
- Well, I already know
I'm not invited.

39:41.767 --> 39:43.266
- Okay, so why'd you ask?

39:43.300 --> 39:45.000
Are you trying to start
something with me?

39:45.033 --> 39:47.133
- I already know, like,
ten years from now--

39:47.166 --> 39:48.467
- You're probably not
gonna be here in a month, hon.

39:48.500 --> 39:49.600
Sorry.
- All right.

39:49.633 --> 39:51.066
I don't plan on going anywhere.

39:51.100 --> 39:52.600
So get used to me.
- Okay, well--

39:52.633 --> 39:54.200
- Yeah. I see those children
more than you see them.

39:54.200 --> 39:57.133
[dramatic music]

39:58.500 --> 40:01.033
- Kathryn, there was
an overwhelming response

40:01.066 --> 40:03.734
from viewers about, uh, how you
handled yourself in Hilton Head.

40:03.767 --> 40:07.166
"Wow, Kathryn exercised
incredible restrain.

40:07.200 --> 40:09.133
"I would have punched Ashley
in the face.

40:09.166 --> 40:11.200
"Those words to a mother
hurt deeply,

40:11.233 --> 40:12.667
"especially one that's
recovering

40:12.700 --> 40:14.600
