I--I see it.

40:21.600 --> 40:23.100
- Tell me about it.
What's wrong with them?

40:23.100 --> 40:24.734
- First of all,
they don't sleep.

40:24.767 --> 40:27.100
- Because they see me
for two days.

40:27.133 --> 40:28.600
- Well, that's what's
even scarier,

40:28.633 --> 40:30.233
is you're gonna start
getting more time with them.

40:30.266 --> 40:33.033
Yeah.
- Whoa, dude.

40:33.066 --> 40:34.633
- I mean, it brought tears
to my eyes.

40:34.633 --> 40:36.734
I mean, I sat there
and cried when she left,

40:36.767 --> 40:38.300
because I just couldn't imagine

40:38.333 --> 40:41.100
hearing the things that she said
and being,

40:41.100 --> 40:43.100
you know, a mother
and loving her two children.

40:43.133 --> 40:45.633
I just imagine
how I would handle that.

40:45.667 --> 40:47.500
- I just remember

40:47.500 --> 40:49.300
Danni was talking to me,
and so I was just

40:49.333 --> 40:53.300
holding Kathryn's hand,
and she was trembling.

40:53.333 --> 40:55.600
- How did you
keep your composure?

40:55.633 --> 40:57.266
- I was thinking about,
like, my kids.

40:57.300 --> 40:59.233
Like, I mean,
they're more important than

40:59.266 --> 41:01.633
ever responding to someone who's
throwing accusations out there.

41:01.667 --> 41:05.100
- Cameran, as a new mom,
what was your reaction?

41:05.133 --> 41:07.200
- I didn't go to Hilton Head.
I watched as a viewer.

41:07.233 --> 41:09.066
And I just sat there
with my mouth wide open.

41:09.100 --> 41:12.600
I couldn't--
I couldn't believe it.

41:12.633 --> 41:15.667
- Kathryn, Chelsea
went as far as to say

41:15.667 --> 41:18.133
that Thomas and Ashley
weren't allowed back

41:18.166 --> 41:20.266
in the house if
it made you feel uncomfortable.

41:20.266 --> 41:22.333
- Yeah.
And I--I appreciated that.

41:22.367 --> 41:24.266
I mean, it was scary
what happened.

41:24.266 --> 41:26.000
- I was terrified.

41:26.033 --> 41:27.633
