a little brainwashed.

1:00:59.667 --> 1:01:03.066
And I guess that's what I get
for judging Kathryn.

1:01:03.100 --> 1:01:05.333
I mean, Erin, it was even hard,
I mean--

1:01:05.367 --> 1:01:08.000
apologizing, like.
[sighs]

1:01:08.033 --> 1:01:10.300
I mean, maybe I didn't
make a clear enough apology,

1:01:10.300 --> 1:01:12.767
but I still stood by
what I said.

1:01:13.000 --> 1:01:15.533
It is really hard

1:01:15.567 --> 1:01:17.233
to have walked in there
and feel like

1:01:17.266 --> 1:01:20.300
have--having no support,
you know?

1:01:20.333 --> 1:01:23.133
Because I don't--I think
Thomas deserves that too.

1:01:23.166 --> 1:01:25.033
He's my best friend, and

1:01:25.066 --> 1:01:27.567
I'm not ready
to throw in the towel,

1:01:27.600 --> 1:01:30.400
despite what
everybody else says.

1:01:30.433 --> 1:01:33.100
I'm really happy.

1:01:33.133 --> 1:01:35.166
And, like, I said...

1:01:37.066 --> 1:01:38.300
- No.

1:01:38.300 --> 1:01:41.033
- In three, two...

1:01:41.066 --> 1:01:43.533
- We're back with
our final moments

1:01:43.567 --> 1:01:45.567
with the group from
"Southern Charm."

1:01:45.567 --> 1:01:47.133
This season, there's been

1:01:47.166 --> 1:01:49.667
a lot of dramatic ebbs and flows

1:01:49.700 --> 1:01:51.600
and a hurricane named Ashley

1:01:51.633 --> 1:01:53.667
that blew the wind out of
everyone's sails.

1:01:53.700 --> 1:01:56.300
But the one thing
that's remained constant

1:01:56.333 --> 1:01:59.266
is the solid friendship
between these charmers.

