- Kathryn, you've allowed
cameras into your life

1:03:15.300 --> 1:03:16.734
over the past five seasons

1:03:16.767 --> 1:03:19.133
at the most personal, emotional,

1:03:19.133 --> 1:03:21.400
and heartbreaking times.

1:03:21.400 --> 1:03:24.100
And, uh, you've
come out of it on top.

1:03:24.133 --> 1:03:26.667
And I think you deserve
a round of applause

1:03:26.700 --> 1:03:28.533
for your restraint and...
- Hey!

1:03:28.533 --> 1:03:30.100
[applause]
- Your change this season.

1:03:30.133 --> 1:03:31.500
I mean, honestly.

1:03:31.533 --> 1:03:35.266
Um, Austen, how long till we see
your beer on tap

1:03:35.300 --> 1:03:36.533
at a Charleston bar?

1:03:36.533 --> 1:03:38.066
- [sighs] Gosh, well.

1:03:38.100 --> 1:03:39.533
A couple more hoops
I need to jump through,

1:03:39.533 --> 1:03:42.333
but let's hope for end
of summer, beginning of fall.

